    "The proposal would, given its industrial aesthetic, appear incongruous within its setting, creating a disorderly low quality aesthetic, which would be adverse to the visual amenity of the locality. The proposal would therefore fail to accord with  Policy D4 of the London Plan 2021, Policy 26 of the Havering Local Plan 2016, and the objectives of the NPPF.",
